name: People of Crypto #003 - CZ
description:
CZ aka Changpeng Zhao, is the founder and current CEO of Binance, the largest cryptocurrency in the world by trading volume. Started his career working with a subcontractor for Tokyo Stock Exchange. Founded Fusion System, at the moment is the fastest trading system for brokers. Becoming CTO for OKCoin for a while right before became Binance founder. 

But one of the most interesting fact is he once worked for McDonald's during his teenage years.

Minted on 2021, Oct 7th, will burn all unsold on Oct 14th.
